& .specify/scripts/powershell/create-new-feature.ps1 -Json 'Review my Constitution at .specify/memory/constitution.md and improve it:\n\n1. Are all standards testable (not vague)?\n   - \u274c Vague: \"Papers should be well-written\"\n   - \u2705 Testable: \"Flesch-Kincaid grade 10-12; active voice 75%+ of time\"\n\n2. Did I cover essential categories?\n   - Citation accuracy\n   - Source verification\n   - Writing clarity\n   - Plagiarism checking\n   - Review process\n\n3. Are any standards unrealistic?\n\nSuggest 2-3 concrete improvements.' -Number 1 -ShortName 'constitution-review' 'Review constitution and suggest improvements based on given criteria.'